	.string "Dear, what do you think of this?\n"
	.string "Wouldn't this make a nice gift?\p"
	.string "It's…PRO…TE…IN?\n"
	.string "It sounds delicious, doesn't it?$"

BattleFrontier_Mart_Text_FacilitiesDontAllowItems:
